## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **pramipexole Mirapex 2006** = first FDA DA agonist RLS — D3 preference (D3>D2>D4). 만성 long-term augmentation 부작용 paradigm shift 직전 era. quantum-VQE 의 D3 GPCR pocket 직접 fit (cross-parkinson DA agonist 일부 동일).
2. **ropinirole Requip 2005 + rotigotine patch Neupro 2012** = second/third DA agonist. ropinirole = 만성 oral D2/D3 non-ergot. rotigotine = transdermal 24h continuous (만성 augmentation 회피 + steady-state plasma).
3. **gabapentin enacarbil Horizant 2011** = first FDA α2δ RLS prodrug. gabapentin 의 absorption variability 해결 (LAT1 transporter) + 만성 augmentation 회피. AASM 2024 guideline 의 1L (DA agonist 후순위 shift).
4. **gabapentin + pregabalin off-label** = 만성 off-label α2δ. pregabalin Phase 3 RCT (Allen 2014) positive — 그러나 FDA RLS indication 미승인. 만성 long-term tolerability 가 DA agonist 보다 우수.
5. **iron deficiency + ferric carboxymaltose Injectafer + 만성 IV iron** = 만성 RLS 의 iron deficiency 가 substrate (BTBD9 + MEIS1 GWAS + brain iron deficit). serum ferritin <75 ng/mL 또는 transferrin saturation <20% 시 IV iron 1L. cross-nutritional_pharmacology + chronic_kidney_disease.
6. **augmentation phenomenon paradigm** = DA agonist 만성 long-term 후 dose 증가 paradox + 증상 이른 발현 + 증상 영역 확대 (다리 → 팔 + 몸통). pramipexole + ropinirole + levodopa 의 ergot legacy + non-ergot 모두 augmentation. 만성 paradigm shift = α2δ 1L + 만성 opioid refractory.
7. **oxycodone + buprenorphine + methadone 만성 augmentation refractory** = MOR opioid 만성 refractory salvage. RLS-1 Buprenorphine RCT (2024) positive. 만성 dependence + abuse 위험 vs RLS QoL 임상 trade-off.
8. **clonazepam + zolpidem + eszopiclone off-label** = 만성 sleep + secondary off-label. dependence + falls (cross-geriatric Beers Criteria 부적합). 1L 아님.
9. **dipyridamole (research)** = adenosine A2A 만성 — Garcia-Borreguero 2021 Phase 2 RCT positive. mechanism = 만성 adenosine signaling alteration (A1+A2A). 만성 next-gen non-DA + non-α2δ paradigm 가능성.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, RLS 임상 의미 한정.

